{
 "name": "RPlog_Orson_s_Wild_Ride",
 "title": "Orson's Wild Ride",
 "summary": "In the cleared central area of Karrde's base on Myrkr, the mechanic Orson takes the Jedi Jessalyn Valios along on a characteristically chaotic outing aboard one of his tinkered craft. When the ship's repulsor systems misbehave mid-flight, leaving them spinning lazily in space on emergency lighting, the unflappable Orson cheerfully whistles his way through the repairs, reading the tangle of pipes and wires like a scholar reads a book. Jessalyn follows him aft, helping check scorched power nodes as the two troubleshoot together. The misadventure blends Orson's mechanical genius with the easy camaraderie between him and Jessalyn.",
